The paper focuses on active learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). It also deals with multi-view learning, which involves multiple subsets of features (views), making it relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions Web page classification and advertisement removal, which fall under information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper uses empirical evaluation, which is common in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
